ape2paleoPhylo          Convert objects of class 'phylo' to class
                        'paleoPhylo'.
as.paleoPhylo           The 'paleoPhylo' class.
berggren95              W.A. Berggren's 1995 geologic timescale
createBifurcate         Create a fully bifurcating object of class
                        'phylo'.
css                     Calculate Corrected Survivorship Scores.
drawPhylo               Plot a lineage phylogeny.
gradstein04             Gradstein et al.'s 2004 Geologic Time Scale.
paleoPhylo-package      Biodiversity Analyses in a Paleontological and
                        Phylogenetic Context
pearson93               An example lineage phylogeny.
prune.to.date           Returns the phylogeny of the clade to some
                        cut-off point.
pruneTree               Prune a tree.
rwb                     Calculate per-lineage origination and
                        extinction rates within a set of bins
stratUnc                Include stratigraphic uncertainty in paleoPhylo
                        plots.
timeAxis                Plot a time axis to append to, e.g., diversity
                        curve plots.
